{"tid":2498232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"MIRROR演唱會｜新入職「表兄弟」賣飛收款後失蹤　六同事失10萬元","createTime":"2021-04-21T04:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T04:45:10.000Z","uid":302200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2207361a4eee0068796ac022a736a2f38b8bebb1","tid":2498232,"uid":302200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"男團MIRROR演唱會將於下月舉行，惟開賣已火速售罄，一票難求，有六名「鏡粉」更於職場被騙。<br />\n有苦主向《香港01》投訴，指公司一對新入職的「表兄弟」，自稱與娛樂圈人士相熟，可為同事以正價購入MIRROR演唱會門票，惟收款近10萬元後失聯，不再上班又搬離住處，疑已捲款潛逃。<br />\n警方回覆指，於4月16日及19日接獲兩名女子報案，案件列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」，暫未有人被捕。《香港01》正向ViuTV及MIRROR經理人黃慧君（花姐）查詢事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2021/04/21/jPyICm.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2021%2F04%2F21%2FjPyICm.jpeg&h=23634c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01偵查/614513/mirror演唱會-新入職-表兄弟-賣飛收款後失蹤-六同事失10萬元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5%2F614513%2Fmirror%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83-%E6%96%B0%E5%85%A5%E8%81%B7-%E8%A1%A8%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F-%E8%B3%A3%E9%A3%9B%E6%94%B6%E6%AC%BE%E5%BE%8C%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-%E5%85%AD%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%B110%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=2bed0dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01偵查/614513/mirror演唱會-新入職-表兄弟-賣飛收款後失蹤-六同事失10萬元</a>"},{"pid":"75a25c6c1c7f8ddc20c68c86b963076b5786dbf2","tid":2498232,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9aaa5a6cbddee896bc5d622d40bc3eb4391690","tid":2498232,"uid":87582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"公司亦曾派員到他們的住所了解，發現二人已搬走，屋內只剩垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n都幾痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dde2469ad10d